Date: Wed, 24 Jun 2026 08:43:59 +1000
Subject: [PATCH] =?UTF-8?q?0027:=20/config=20polish=20=E2=80=94=20live=20m?=
 =?UTF-8?q?odel=20in=20/queue=20caps=20+=20atomic=20swap=20under=20RLock?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=20(#6)?=
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
